Orlando Jones https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Orlando_Jones 0 Orlando Jones (born April 10, 1968) is an American comedian and actor. He is known for being one of the original cast members of the sketch comedy series MADtv and for his role as the 7 Up spokesman from 1999 to 2002.
